            {
               "text": "### Prerequisites\n\nTo better understand this text, we recommend reading the first three chapters of the section *First Steps*, as well as the first chapter of the section *Understanding Texts*",
               "source": [
                  {
                     "type": 1,
                     "uuid": "b5efc8f9-c268-430f-9681-7a43848ee48e",
                     "text": "History Tracers Team, First Steps",
                     "date_time": {
                        "type": "",
